 <description>The desert Fathers post three Wrong Way signs on the road to Christian living.  The signs keep us from believing that (1) The body is evil, (2) Fasting, prayer and other spiritual practices are "ends in themselves" and (3) We can "earn" our way to heaven by doing good works!   This podcast will keep us on a spiritually safe road if we obey the Wrong Way signs God has posted for our protection.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
