      <title>Desert Spirituality for City Folks - Part 8âThe Journey</title>
      <link>http://feeds.ancientfaith.com/~r/SimplyOrthodox/~3/sEwy7MAOpwE/desert_spirituality_for_city_folks_part_8_the_journey</link>
